THIS REPOSITORY USES A BACKEND SUBMODULE

The backend for this project is managed as a git submodule and configured in .gitmodules.

To initialize and update the submodule locally run:

  git submodule sync --recursive
  git submodule update --init --recursive

If you prefer embedding the backend into this repo (not as a submodule), contact the maintainer to merge the backend source directly into the backend/ directory and remove the submodule metadata.
